<h2>What we are</h2>
<p>Sarga Technologies makes an ideal Partner for organizations looking for the IT solutions because of its core capabilities in technology, great man power and commitments to the quality. The belief in Sarga, "No compromise on the quality at any cost" empowers the clients to trust us on the quality. It offers the range of services to the clients in the area of Consulting, Development/Integration, Testing services and Training. </p>
<p>Sarga, with more than 5 years of experience in product development in the area of automative and control systems has a good number of client base.
Clients are well benifited from the unwavering focus, approach and the leadership qualities which Sarga technologies exhibits through out. </p>
<p>With the Leadership in Technology, Sarga Technologies building the Trust And being a core technology and product company Sarga Technologies is delivering enhanced business perfrmance with its innovations.</p>

